{"tid":752704,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［賭波有圖］問過足球賽馬資訊監管，依間tips信唔信得過","createTime":"2018-07-23T04:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T12:36:34.000Z","uid":181406,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f03940b5069aa5d8f752563c53d91c4481c8c413","tid":752704,"uid":181406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheSoccerHelper2688/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheSoccerHelper2688%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=7PxwOGkTbeXZjwJBTQNWwV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=1751fb26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TheSoccerHelper2688/?ref=page_internal</a><br />\n<br />\n上邊條link係足球賽馬資訊監管介紹嘅，佢就話會有唔錯回報，又聲稱唔收錢做過60天乜撚認證，認證過d貼士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/123026_1f9ac2768830f200a4d7fe30b48e4da8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F123026_1f9ac2768830f200a4d7fe30b48e4da8.png&h=a4eac259&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/123027_1f9ac2768830f200a4d7fe30b48e4da8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F123027_1f9ac2768830f200a4d7fe30b48e4da8.png&h=4cfd52f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/123648_4c8e31fe450447008d020b69590e982d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F123648_4c8e31fe450447008d020b69590e982d.png&h=6b9d8420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴/絲打真心試過依間咩Soccer Helper，定係大家都覺得係騙子，因為我知道坊間騙子多到數唔到，但係嗰個足球賽馬資訊監管話行內人先知邊間信得過，佢就介紹咗依間俾我，定係根本個咩足球監管都係所謂嘅騙子，不喜勿插，想大家研究下<br />\n<br />\n足球監管條link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/Honest-%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E8%B3%BD%E9%A6%AC%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E5%89%B5%E5%A7%8B%E7%BE%A4-1935924670018310/\" data-s